  "texts": [
    "Building a Pool of Examples.In some cases, obtaining a limited amount of sensor data with the associated ground truth (ADLs) may be possible.",
    "For example, a technician may perform annotation during an initial calibration phase of the system, or some limited dataset collected in similar settings as the deployment target may become available.",
    "Let D be this dataset composed of a set of pairs (𝑤, 𝐴) where 𝑤 is a window of raw sensor data, while 𝐴 is the corresponding activity label.",
    "We convert D to a set E called Pool of Examples.",
    "This set contains the textual representation of the windows in D (leveraging Window2Text) associated with the corresponding activity label."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}